<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <!-- Poner % titulo %> aca   -->
    <title>Titulo</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/gordo-colombes-logo" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/articulo.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("navbar")-%>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-articulo text-center">
        <h1 id="titulo-articulo"><strong><%=articulo.title%></strong></h1>
        <h4 id="autor-articulo" class="mt-4">
          Creado por <%= articulo.authorId%>. Fecha de publicaci√≥n: <%=
          articulo.createdAt %>
        </h4>
      </div>

      <div id="articulo">
        <div>
          <div id="img-articulo">
            <img
              src="/img/<%=articulo.image%>"
              alt="img"
              class="img-fluid shadow-lg"
              id="img-individual"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="contenido-articulo">
          <p><%= articulo.content %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="mt-5" />
      <div id="area-comentarios" class="mt-2">
        <h3>Comentarios</h3>
        <form action="">
          <textarea
            type="text"
            placeholder="Deja tu comentario..."
            name="comment-box"
            id="comment-box"
            class="form-control mt-4"
          >
          </textarea>
          <div
            id="btn-enviar"
            class="mt-2 d-flex justify-content-end align-items-center"
          >
            <a href="" class="btn btn-dark">Enviar</a>
          </div>
        </form>
        <div id="comment" class="mt-5">
          <div class="row mb-2">
            <div id="comment-user" class="mb-2">Usuario</div>
            <div id="comment-date" class="mb-2">Fecha</div>
          </div>
          <p id="comment-content">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi hic
            alias nisi ut porro enim deserunt quo officiis omnis deleniti! Quasi
            dolorum at vitae nemo eaque ducimus? Aliquam, veniam aspernatur.
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quam
            tempore voluptatum tenetur, quo assumenda quia facilis fuga iure
            minus corporis nisi ipsa perferendis dolores quod rerum nam saepe
            laboriosam ad.
          </p>

          <hr />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("footer")-%>
  </body>
</html>
